summary: Adds that one asshole from oblivion to the whiterun prison cell you keep getting sent to when you accidentally steal a kettle. You can release all the anger you feel towards the whiterun guards onto this guy.
descriptionHtml: Adds that one asshole from oblivion to the whiterun prison cell you keep getting sent to when you accidentally steal a kettle. You can release all the anger you feel towards the whiterun guards onto this guy. He isn't connected to any crime faction so you won't get in trouble.
author: SatansFetusLegs
